transcripts.text: Dallas, Stephen Darby Ministries presents Back to Fellowship Conference, a day of powerful worship and genuine fellowship.  Saturday, June 1st, 2019, 1 p.m.  to 4 p.m.  at the Dallas Marriott Suites Medical Market Center, 2493 North Stevens Freeway, Dallas, Texas, 75207.  There will be a $25 registration fee.  For hotel and additional information, please visit www.stephendarbyministries.com.
